high_descs: Go to the counter on the left of the sink.
Pick up the yellow knife on the counter.
Turn left to go to the black round table next to the wall.
Slice the tomato on the table in front of the tea kettle.
Place the knife on the top of the spatula on the table.
Pick up one slice of the tomato.
Turn right to go to the front of the refrigerator.
Chill the tomato slice on the top shelf in the refrigerator and take it out.
Turn right to go to the counter with the microwave on the other side of the kitchen.
Place the tomato slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of tomato in the microwave.

high_descs: Move to the right and forward to stand in front of the sink to the left of the sink.
Pick the larger knife on the right up from the counter.
Go left and then turn to the left to face the round, black table.
Slice the tomato on the table.
Put the knife down on the table.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the table.
Turn around and stand in front of the fridge.
Put the tomato slice in the fridge and shut the door and then open the door, take the tomato slice out and shut the door again.
Go right and cross the room to face the microwave.
Put the tomato slice in the microwave and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Slice a tomato and put the chilled slice into the microwave.

high_descs: Go to the counter right of the stove
Pick up the knife
Go to the round black table
Cut the tomato
Put the knife down on the table
Pick up a tomato slice
Go to the fridge
Chill the tomato
Go to the microwave
Put the tomato slice in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled tomato slice in the microwave
